      <userestrict id="aspace_816412aed753015f43d5c7d6d63f18eb">
         <head>Conditions Governing Use</head>
         <p>The Francis M. Dimond Mier Expedition Papers are the physical property of the Beinecke Rare Book and Manuscript Library, Yale University. Literary rights, including copyright, belong to the authors or their legal heirs and assigns. For further information, consult the appropriate curator.</p>  
