      </accessrestrict>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_68b36e3e78578c12d1bbbd41f65fb13a">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Francis M. Dimond was United States Consul at Vera Cruz, Mexico. The bulk of the collection consists of letters to Francis Dimond concerning members of the Mier Expedition held prisoner in Perote, Mexico.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
